    <string name="str_fas_is_a_user_space_implementa">i-FAS iwukuqaliswa kwendawo yomsebenzisi ye-FAS (Frame Aware Scheduling), enenzuzo yokuhambisana cishe kwendawo yonke nokuvumelana nezimo kunoma iyiphi idivayisi uma iqhathaniswa ne-MI FEAS yendawo ye-kernel. I-FAS (Frame Aware Scheduling) yilo mqondo wokuhlela, ozama ukulawula ukusebenza ngokuqapha ukunikezwa kwesithonjana ukuze kuncishiswe umthwalo oqhubekayo ngenkathi kuqinisekiswa isikhathi sokunikeza.</string>
    <string name="str_frame_aware_scheduling">Ukuhlela Okuqaphela Isithonjana</string>
    <string name="str_fpsgo_frame_per_second_go_is_a">I-FPSGO (Frame Per Second GO) iyimoduli ye-kernel ye-MediaTek eguqula ngokuguquguqukayo amaza e-CPU/GPU ngokusekelwe kumazinga esithonjana esikhathi sangempela. Ukuyivula kusiza ukulondoloza impilo yebhethri futhi kunciphisa ukushisa ngokwehlisa ukusebenza ngesikhathi sezithonjana ezinzile.</string>
    <string name="str_app_specific_settings_will_ove">Izilungiselelo eziqondene nohlelo zizobhala phezu kwezilungiselelo zomhlaba wonke. Zishiye ziyimisiwe ukuze zizuze izilungiselelo zomhlaba wonke.</string>
